window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When a fiendish fraudster has been fomenting financial falsehoods, who can find the finagler?</p> <p>The World’s Greatest Detective Agency, of course!</p> <p>Staffed by the eccentric man who calls himself Sherman Holmes and aided by his ever-composed assistant Watson, the duo will take on cases other agencies might consider helpless, hopeless, or downright preposterous.</p> <p>Which is how our fearless fellows find themselves investigating a Renaissance faire’s cooked books, with the finger of guilt pointing directly at their client. To prove his innocence, Sherman and Watson will have to join the revelry, triumph in challenges, deal with an unusually aggressive parrot, and uncover the true origins of the seemingly cheerful faire.</p>"; 
